   "body" : "If user has X bitcoins in encrypted wallet and wants to send them all, and transaction would require fee, here is how\r\napplication logic goes right now:\r\n\r\n1. Put address and X bitcoins into appropriate fields then click on \"Send\" button.\r\n2. Confirm send action.\r\n3. Type password and proceed.\r\n4. Bitcoin-qt will complain about not having enough bitcoins to pay fee.\r\n\r\nSteps 3. and 4. should be reversed. Additionaly, step where client asks user if he or she is OK with paying extra fee\r\ndue to young coins and / or transaction size should come before typing password.",
